text: John Ossowski (born 10 February 1962) is a Canadian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Etobicoke Category:Rowers from Toronto
